race.comment: RAINLINE (11) was knocking on the door prior to last start where she got there right on time, winning in a photo. Pike remains in the saddle today as she drops back in trip to Wednesday company. She's likely to be back from the draw but she can storm over the top to go back-to-back. SIR DREAMALOT (1) drops right back in grade today and the last time we saw him at 1400m he was only beaten 1.5L in a Listed event. That stands right out against this field, though the query will be whether he's going as good now. The 3kg claim helps and if he can improve now, he's a serious threat. ISHKUR (9) gets the winkers on first time today after finishing 1.7L behind the impressive Fast Harry last time out. Maps for a lovely run under Fiore and she can put her best foot forward. AMAZING CHEAT (5) can resume on a positive note. SPARKLE CORNER (7) will appreciate the rise in trip and won't be far away.
